name: petStarLABS : etch-A-scope
description:
petStar Interactive presents : etch-A-scope

Had a few of these petStar tablets lying around and decided to wire them up into oscilloscopes ! 
Hope u find some use in these old proto-types.. They could use some luvv. 


~how~
click = clear + draw
Right click = pause mouse

1 - grav
2 - animate
3 - mmmmulti
4 - afterDark
5 - disposableFlash
6 - slowLine


PLZ NOTE-= this experience works best in a window + not in full screen. However i have not found a way from stopping u from doing *u* 

Shoutout to @katecursed for the inspo :D
+ for beta testers for the feedback

Hope you all enjoy ! _ and let me know if this doesn’t work on your browser/ device. if you need a refund, just hmu. This software is experimental + i welcome all feedback. 

Oh, and PLZ!  SNE DME YOUR LIGHT DRAWINGS. Godspeed fools 
<3 - chippy
